Street lighting decreases possible night accidents by enhancing visibility. They also assist in making pedestrians and motorists more aware of possible dangers, such as hijacking and robbery. It provides a safe and crime-free environment. Residents are encouraged to report a streetlight when: Contact the municipal call centre to report on 013 243 1806, 013 249 7714/7348/7344/7349, 0878087430 and WhatsApp 064 915 3362.